        <h1>Why flagging a risk early strengthens delivery trust.</h1>
        <p class="lede">A late surprise makes the other person carry uncertainty they could have planned for. An early warning gives them choices.</p>
        <p class="article-meta"><span class="review-badge">Draft for review</span><span>By Scott Hunter</span><span>7 minute read</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-visual" role="img" aria-label="A risk is seen and flagged early, allowing the plan to change">
