        <span class="signal-node signal-node--two">Flag<br />early</span>
        <span class="signal-node signal-node--three">Plan<br />changes</span>
        <blockquote>“The issue is rarely that the news was difficult. It is that the other person heard it too late to act.”</blockquote>
